<br>
You bastard Rangers are NOT like me. Not in the least.<br>
I care not how many people you killed, how you enjoy killing, or how 'evil' you think you are. Because the fact of the matter is, you are just animals. The Lion kills, the Tiger kills, the little wolf kills. These worthless creatons are not evil, and neither are you.<br>
<br>
Chaos.. It is not something that is restricted to Evil people, or Good people, or people on some 'Path to Power'. Chaotic Behavor has been displayed in many, even the Paladin Gavin and the Monk Ayamamii before she died showed the Chaotic Behavor. Does this make one evil?<br>
<br>
Nay. It does not. I am on my Dark Path of Chaos. This is for those that enjoy killing for the sake of evilness. To hurt and be cruel to others. To destroy familes and cause tears and sorry.<br>
<br>
Most of you 'Power Seekers' are just that. Neutralic power seekers. You enjoy fighting, and will kill anything that suits you at the time. I could pay one of you bastards to kill Tunare if I had enought platium. You are people without loyality. My loyality lies with the Pathways of Darkness. Fear, Hate, War, and Death.<br>
You have no loyality execpt to yourselves. So don't get bend out of shape when I kill you like the Elven Ranger that you are. Or Dwarven Rogue that you are, or whatever you are.<br>
<br>
Then the Rarity.. but their are those that enjoy taking Darkness from the world by death. Those like Gavin and Banegrivm, the Paladins of Chaos. They are not like me, execpt for the fact that they fight instead of acting like the Weak Pathetic Kimaya, who only tries to bring peace and offer cookies and various other things that have no value.<br>
<br>
A world of Chaos is just that. A world Dominated by US, the Children of Chaos.The ShadowKnight and the Paladin, locked in combat.. instead of.. people falling for the Peaceful Orderly ways of ..to use her as an example once again.. Kimaya.<br>
<br>
A world of Battle, and fighting.. and killing. Everyone goes in, only one side comes out. Thus is the way of Chaos.<br>
<br>
This does not mean I am your brother in Chaos. Stop acting like it. You know who I am talking about, and I have NOTHING to learn from you, bastard. You'll die.<br>
<br>
Kage no Adakia, The Darkness of Chaos. That is what I shall bring to those that dare stand in my way, or were born looking at me wrong.<br>
<br>
That is all.<br>
